# Lore-friendly broadcast variants (picked at random)
# Alliance announcements
st-faction-relations-alliance-1 = Stalkers, got word from a reliable source. {$factionA} and {$factionB} shook hands. They are allies now. Plan your routes accordingly.
st-faction-relations-alliance-2 = Hey, listen up. {$factionA} and {$factionB} made a pact. Full alliance. Could change the balance of power in the Zone.
st-faction-relations-alliance-3 = Big news, brothers. {$factionA} and {$factionB} joined forces. If you are not with them, better watch your back out there.
st-faction-relations-alliance-4 = Just picked up chatter on the radio. {$factionA} and {$factionB} are working together now. Stay sharp, stalker.

# Neutral announcements
st-faction-relations-neutral-1 = Looks like {$factionA} and {$factionB} cooled things down. Back to neutral. Do not get too comfortable though.
st-faction-relations-neutral-2 = Word around the campfire is {$factionA} and {$factionB} agreed to stop shooting each other. For now at least.
st-faction-relations-neutral-3 = {$factionA} and {$factionB} settled their beef. Relations are neutral. I would not count on it lasting, but that is the Zone for you.
st-faction-relations-neutral-4 = Some trader told me {$factionA} and {$factionB} called a truce. Neutral terms. Keep your head on a swivel anyway.

# Hostile announcements
st-faction-relations-hostile-1 = Watch yourselves out there. {$factionA} and {$factionB} are hostile now. Patrols might get twitchy.
st-faction-relations-hostile-2 = Bad blood between {$factionA} and {$factionB}. Hostilities confirmed. If you are caught between them, that is your problem.
st-faction-relations-hostile-3 = Heads up, stalkers. {$factionA} and {$factionB} turned on each other. Stay clear of their turf if you can.
st-faction-relations-hostile-4 = Things went south between {$factionA} and {$factionB}. They are hostile. Could get messy near the borders.

# War announcements
st-faction-relations-war-1 = All stalkers, this is serious. {$factionA} and {$factionB} are at war. Steer clear of the frontlines or you will end up in a body bag.
st-faction-relations-war-2 = Full-scale war between {$factionA} and {$factionB}. They are shooting on sight. If you value your life, stay out of it.
st-faction-relations-war-3 = The Zone just got a lot more dangerous, brothers. {$factionA} and {$factionB} declared war. Blood is going to flow.
st-faction-relations-war-4 = Open warfare between {$factionA} and {$factionB}. They are killing anything that moves near their lines. You have been warned, stalker.
